	(text "Want to protect internal logic from voltage fluctuations\non VDD line from LEDs changing brightness; this is max. \n2 kHz fluctuations, so want to make a high-pass filter. \n\nWant to use a small cap. (50-150 nF) for fast response, then ~375Ω \nresistor to filter out noise w/ periods lower than 20 ms"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
